OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will stay
OL,6,Fcloudier in the west with scattered
OL,7,Fshowers feeding in. Generally drier
OL,8,Fwith some bright then clear spells in
OL,9,Fthe east. Windy at times.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSaturday:FIt will stay mainly dry in
OL,12,Fthe east with some bright spells at
OL,13,Ftimes. Mostly cloudy in the west with
OL,14,Fsome showers. Windy at times.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FDry and
OL,17,Fincreasingly sunny on Sunday. Dry and
OL,18,Fbright start on Monday, perhaps
OL,19,Fcloudier towards the coast, rain from
OL,20,Fsouthwest later. Mostly cloudy Tuesday
OL,21,Fwith rain or showers. Becoming warmer.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
